  ('3b41acaf-58f3-11f1-bd30-cc28aac91a8b', 'c288424d-c135-426e-afa5-a72040ae6476', 'Transmission Network Asset Mapping and Predictive Utility GIS System', 'A regional power distribution utility invites proposals for implementation of a geospatial asset management and predictive maintenance system for transmission and distribution infrastructure. The project aims to create a centralized GIS-based utility network model integrating substations, transformers, transmission lines, smart meters, and outage management systems. The selected vendor will conduct field data collection, GPS-based asset validation, drone-assisted corridor inspections, and integration of SCADA and IoT sensor feeds. The solution should support predictive analytics for asset failure detection, vegetation encroachment analysis, line-loss mapping, and outage impact visualization.', '250000.00', 'closed', NULL, '2026-05-26 11:08:31', '2026-06-27 18:30:00', '2027-04-11 18:30:00', '2026-05-20 00:46:00', 'public', 'Test2pdf', 'test90@gmail.com', '["/uploads/proposals/1778519814976-Utility_Power_RFP.pdf"]', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'v1.0'),
